<h1>“一次真正的对话”：布林肯在中国进行“建设性”会谈</h1>
<p>Author: 半岛电视台＋通讯社</p>
<p>Publisher: Al Jazeera</p>
<p>Published Time: 2023-06-19T-4:40:47</p>
<p>Modified Time: 2023-06-19T05:40:47</p>
<p>Description: 美国高级外交官在北京会见中国外长，这是五年来双方最高级别的正式访问。</p>
<p>Images: ["<a href="https://chinese.aljazeera.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/21-1687152504.jpg">21-1687152504...</a>", "<a href="https://chinese.aljazeera.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/22-1687152510.jpg">22-1687152510...</a>", "<a href="https://chinese.aljazeera.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/23-1687152516.jpg">23-1687152516...</a>", "<a href="https://chinese.aljazeera.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/24-1687152522.jpg">24-1687152522...</a>", "<a href="https://chinese.aljazeera.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/25-1687152529.jpg">25-1687152529...</a>"]</p>
